.TH SG-DAEMON 1 "June 2026" "Snoop Guard 1.1.0-dev"
.SH NAME
sg-daemon \- monitor webcam and microphone activity
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B sg-daemon
[\fB--config\fR \fIPATH\fR] [\fB--version\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Runs in the user session, publishes org.snoopguard.Service on D-Bus, and sends
notifications when camera or microphone capture is detected.
.SH FILES
.I ~/.config/snoop-guard.ini
and
.I ~/.local/state/snoop-guard/events.log
.SH SIGNALS
SIGHUP reloads configuration. SIGINT and SIGTERM stop the daemon.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sg-ctl (1)
